</span></div></section><section class="section sec-homeAbout"><div class="bg-sharp">
<span>
<img data-lazyloaded="1" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=" data-src="https://hanoisignature.vn/wp-content/themes/pixelplus/assets/img/homeAbout-sharp-1.png" alt="">
</span></div><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-md-10 offset-md-1"><div class="titleBox"><div class="wow fadeInUp">
